Package cs213.photoAlbum.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AlbumHash
    Implements methods for the Album class as they relate to the hashtable data structure
    BackEndHash
    This interface allows select elements of the model to interact with other packages of the application.
    PhotoHash
    Photohash implements methods for the Photo class as they relate to the hashmap datastucture
    UserHash
    Userhash implements methods for user as they relate to a hashtable datastructure.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Album
    Object to represent an album and associated data.
    Backend
    Backend holds the top level of the current data structure.
    Photo
    Object to represent an individual photo, will store associated captions, access dates, user tags, etc...
    Tag
    This class will store tag objects for photos.
    User
    Object to represent an individual user, members are package private unless stated otherwise.
